# SDX stage-gate per-project allowlist (REQ-GATE-1).
# One shell glob per line (project-relative path). '#' comments are ignored.
# Empty file = no extra allowance beyond built-in always-allow list.
#
# Built-in always-allow (not configurable): docs/**, .claude/**, *.md
# This file extends that list with project-specific paths that should be
# writable before the Execution gate (e.g., generated files, migrations).
#
# Examples (uncomment and adapt for your project):
# database/migrations/*
# storage/framework/*
# public/build/*

# Meta-repo: plugin manifest is a lifecycle artifact (version bump at Closeout).
.claude-plugin/*
